Recommends:
 docker-ce | docker.io,
 tt-installer
Suggests:
 nvidia-container-toolkit
Description: GTK4 frontend for Tenstorrent AI media generation
 tt-local-generator is a GTK4 desktop application for generating AI videos
 and images using Tenstorrent hardware (Wormhole / Blackhole devices).
 .
 Supports multiple inference backends:
  - Wan2.2-T2V-A14B — text-to-video (QB2 / P300x2 or P150x4)
  - Wan2.2-Animate-14B — character animation (video-to-video)
  - Mochi-1 — alternative video backend
  - FLUX.1-dev — text-to-image
 .
 Includes a three-tier prompt generator (algorithmic, Markov chain, LLM
 polish via Qwen3-0.6B), a playlist / TT-TV channel system, and a
 generation history browser.
 .
 Requires: Docker CE, Tenstorrent firmware + kernel module (via tt-installer),
 and ~118 GB of model weights downloaded from HuggingFace (first-run setup).

Package: tt-model-wan2-t2v
Architecture: all
Depends: tt-local-generator, debconf | debconf-2.0, python3-pip
Description: Wan2.2-T2V-A14B model weights (~118 GB) for tt-local-generator
 Downloads Wan-AI/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B-Diffusers from HuggingFace into
 ~/.cache/huggingface/hub/. Required for the Video generation tab.
 .
 The model is publicly available; a HuggingFace account is not required,
 though providing a token avoids API rate limits.

Package: tt-model-flux
Architecture: all
Depends: tt-local-generator, debconf | debconf-2.0, python3-pip
Description: FLUX.1-dev model weights (~34 GB) for tt-local-generator
 Downloads black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev from HuggingFace. Required for
 the Image generation tab.
 .
 FLUX.1-dev is a gated model — you must accept its license at
 https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev and provide a
 HuggingFace token with read access before installing this package.

Package: tt-model-mochi
Architecture: all
Depends: tt-local-generator, debconf | debconf-2.0, python3-pip
Description: Mochi-1-preview model weights (~20 GB) for tt-local-generator
 Downloads genmo/mochi-1-preview from HuggingFace. Required for the Mochi
 inference backend. The model is publicly available; a HuggingFace account
 is not required.

Package: tt-model-qwen3
Architecture: all
Depends: tt-local-generator, debconf | debconf-2.0, python3-pip
Description: Qwen3-0.6B model weights (~1.2 GB) for tt-local-generator
 Downloads Qwen/Qwen3-0.6B from HuggingFace. Required for the LLM prompt
 polish tier in the prompt-server. The model is fully public; no token
 or license acceptance is required.
